                | For questions about <strong>your order</strong>, contact:
                br
                a(href="mailto:customers.julianocreative@gmail.com")
                    | customers.julianocreative@gmail.com

            p
                | For brands <strong>looking to collaborate</strong>, contact:
                br
                a(href="mailto:collab.julianocreative@gmail.com")
                    | collab.julianocreative@gmail.com



